name: Claimtz
overview:
“Claim your name and secure your Identity on Social Media Networks”

Claimtz services will reserve your name across the social web, and creates full profiles on the most popular social media platforms, to ensure your brand is secured against brandjacking, and safe from social media identity thefts.

Claimtz also provides the opportunity to strengthen the brand identity, and give power to online grow. by having profiles updated on more than 300 social media wensite, brand can connect with their audiance by broadcasting a constant message in the social media crowd, and ensure a positive and legitimate presence over the top ranked social websites.
